# Remove PMT PDF Sidebar
This is a Tampermonkey userscript designed to automatically remove the stupid PDF sidebar on Physics and Maths Tutor (PMT) PDF viewer pages.

## Features
- Automatically removes the sidebar for a cleaner interface.
- Targets pages under the `/pdf-pages/` path of the PMT website.


## Requirements:
- Tampermonkey
- ViolentMonkey ("If your browser does not allow tampermonkey to be installed as an extension, such as Opera GX")

## Installation
1. Install [Tampermonkey](https://www.tampermonkey.net/) for your browser.
2. Click [here](https://github.com/yourusername/Remove-PMT-PDF-Sidebar/raw/main/remove-pmt-pdf-sidebar.user.js) to install the script.
